<br>
The problem with that is that even the epic pet maxes out at level 49. Level 49 aggro radius is very large and will cause aggro to mobs nearby. This prevents the use of pets in a number of raids due to the likelyhood of adds.<br>
<br>
An easy way to see this is to sneak down to the Hole at the pit and summon a pet. As soon as you /pet attack in on a mob, watch the incomming. <p><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=254501">Baron Demar Redfist</A><BR>
