<br>
There are two ways your pet will piss things off now:<br>
1) If they attack it (actually meleeing or casting or taunting it)<br>
2) If a mob receives a call for help from another mob<br>
<br>
Just telling your pet to attack something does not make him kos.  Mobs will not assist each other to kill your pet unless there was actually combat going on at some point.  <br>
