<br>
Call for help range is static per mob.  It doesnt change based on any entity's level. not your pet's, not the enemy's not yours.  Call for help range is always the same for each individual mob no matter who is attacking it.  In the hole, mobs have a particularly high call for help range, if i remember correctly. <p><img src="http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/rhionsligo.jpg" align="center"><br>
